# This repository ships the compiled mods only. Everything is ignored by default; we explicitly allow
# the docs and the mod DLLs. Source, the game's reference DLLs (refs/), decompiled game code (decomp/),
# build output and local tooling are never tracked.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/LICENSE
!/INSTALL.txt
!/mods/
/mods/*
!/mods/*.dll
